# Conventional Commits template
# https://www.conventionalcommits.org/
#
# Types: feat | fix | chore | docs | style | refactor | test | perf | ci
# Scope: project name (optional but recommended)
#
# Examples:
#   feat(agentmesh): add streaming support to gateway
#   fix(agora): handle empty service list gracefully
#   docs: update architecture report with red team findings
#   chore(deps): update fastmcp to 0.6.0
#
# <type>(<scope>): <description>
#
# <body> (optional)
#
# BREAKING CHANGE: <description> (optional)
